Subject: Back end updates
What_We_Know__c:
The Security Backend Updates are related more to the OS on which the EPP server is built(Ubuntu). The Functionality and EPP application upgrades are done from the same section with the Check Now functionality(above Security Backend Updates).

We have also checked and there is sufficient space to apply the backend security updates after accessing the backend of the EPP server.
